title: USModernist in Los Angeles - November 12 + 13!
description:
Join USModernist and USModernist Radio at the Sheats-Goldstein house for a cocktail party November 12, and the next day at the the Stahl House for a Champagne tour. It's a rare chance to see inside these iconic Modernist houses!

Details at www.usmodernist.org/la.
